          "reviewBody": "The number one worst school I have ever seen in chennai so this school is not under mvm group. This school is just making you belive that our school is from mvm group of schools.the worst thing about the school is their white uniform. They tell it has pyjamas. But it look likes chudidhars in white colour without a shawl.and the infrastructure of the school is worst as possible. They do a money collecting business in the name of sports,events and even when they conduct Farwell they ask money from students. For spending money this school thinks a lot. The teachers here are somewhat ok. But my suggestion is that don't put admission for you child in this school.",
